E '''Tambòr''' ta un miembro di e grupo di percussion di [[instrumento]]nan musikal. 

den e hornbostel-sachs classificatione sistema, e ta un membranofone. drums konsistí di por lo menos un membrane, called un drumhead o tambòr kueru, esei ta stretched ariba un kokolishi í struck, either directly ku e player's mannan, o ku un tambòr pega, na produsí zona. tin normalmente un resonance kabes riba e underside di e tambòr, typically tuned na un slightly lower pitch than e top drumhead. otro techniques tin been gewon kausa drums na hasi zona, kon e dùim ròl. drums ta e world's oldest í mas ubiquitous musikal instruments, í e basic diseño ha remained virtually unchanged pa thousands di aña. drums mei ta played individually, ku e player merka un single tambòr, í algun drums kon e djembe ta kasi semper hungado den aki. otronan ta normally played den un aparato di dos o mas, henter played desde e un player, kon bongo drums í timpani. un number di distinto drums huntu ku cymbals forma e basic moderno tambòr kit.

